{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"617","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"全球企業對抗氣候變遷評比出爐 台灣誰獲頂級評等？","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:'>2020-01-20 20:37</span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:'>經濟日報 編譯洪啟原／綜合外電</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E7%A2%B3%E6%8F%AD%E9%9C%B2%E8%A9%95%E9%91%91.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 534px;' /></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'>福特、樂金集團去年在國際碳揭露計畫（<span lang='EN-US'>CDP</span>）的分級中獲得「<span lang='EN-US'>A</span>」評級。路透</span></span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>國際碳揭露計畫（<span lang='EN-US'>CDP</span>）在評比全球<span lang='EN-US'>8,400</span>家企業<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年所揭露資料的對抗氣候變遷行動後，<span lang='EN-US'>20</span>日公布評等清單，共<span lang='EN-US'>179</span>家企業被列為獲得「<span lang='EN-US'>A</span>」頂級評等的「<span lang='EN-US'>A</span>咖名單」，包括美國福特汽車（<span lang='EN-US'>Ford</span>）與微軟（<span lang='EN-US'>Microsoft</span>）、日本<span lang='EN-US'>Sony</span>南韓樂金集團（<span lang='EN-US'>LG</span>）、丹麥樂高集團（<span lang='EN-US'>LEGO</span>）等，被認為最能因應氣候變遷的影響。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>這份<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年報告中，台灣共<span lang='EN-US'>129</span>家企業被評比，台灣大哥大、日月光投資控股、光寶科技、矽品等四家公司獲得「<span lang='EN-US'>A</span>」評等，躋身在氣候數據的透明度、及對抗氣候變遷行動都是頂尖全球企業之林。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>世界先進、元大金融控股、南亞塑膠工業、南亞科技、台塑石化、第一金控、南亞電路板、台達電子、國泰金控、<span lang='EN-US'>UMC </span>聯華電子、福懋興業等台灣企業，則獲得「<span lang='EN-US'>A-</span>」評等，仍是產業領先水準。台積電的評等為「<span lang='EN-US'>B</span>」，代表處於「管理水準」。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>這項報告為<span lang='EN-US'>8,400</span>家公司做分級，評等從「<span lang='EN-US'>A</span>」到「<span lang='EN-US'>D-</span>」，僅<span lang='EN-US'>2%</span>被列入排行頂端的「<span lang='EN-US'>A</span>」評級。「<span lang='EN-US'>A</span>咖名單」除了最新加入的福特、樂金，還有蘋果、<span lang='EN-US'>Google</span>母公司字母（<span lang='EN-US'>Alphabet</span>）、零售業者沃爾瑪（<span lang='EN-US'>Walmart</span>）以及花旗集團（<span lang='EN-US'>Citigroup</span>）、瑞典<span lang='EN-US'>H&amp;M</span>等。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>CDP</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>為非營利組織，鼓勵企業、城市、州來揭露並管理自身對環境的影響；企業股東則利用這項數據評估一家企業是否在這方面有進步。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>以各地來看，名列「<span lang='EN-US'>A</span>咖企業」者以歐洲最多，共<span lang='EN-US'>85</span>家，亞洲有<span lang='EN-US'>51</span>家，北美有<span lang='EN-US'>36</span>家。日本企業首度主宰「<span lang='EN-US'>A</span>咖名單」，共<span lang='EN-US'>38</span>家，多於去年的<span lang='EN-US'>20</span>家。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>CDP</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>表示，「<span lang='EN-US'>A</span>咖企業」被認為氣候數據的透明度、與揭露的完整程度為產業佼佼者，並且在了解氣候風險後，展現強烈的風險治理與管理行動，包括設定以科學為基礎的目標、轉向再生能源、投資低碳產品創新等。<span lang='EN-US'>STOXX</span>的數據也顯示，這些「<span lang='EN-US'>A</span>咖企業」的年度股價表現也比同業高於<span lang='EN-US'>5.5%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://udn.com/news/story/6811/4299110?from=udn-ch1_breaknews-1-cate5-news</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-01-22","clk_count":"167"}},"__N_SSG":true}